<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>Race War will be the Elite PK Server</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Holly Golightly">Holly Golightly</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 6:46 p.m. 6/7/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> Race War will be the Elite PK Server<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Look at this way:

<P>1) How many 15th level warriors can a 25th level wizard take down? Man that is a lot of loot.
<P>2) You get to totally annoy Blue Server people ... for those of you who get a kick out of this kind of thing, Race War is for you!
<P>3) Did I mention 25th level Wizards attacking fully amored and weapon'd 15th level Warriors with impunity?? Root and nuke, root and nuke.
<P>4) Poor Verant ... they are going to petitioned up the wazoo!
<P>This is where a guild like BoL or KAAOS or even The Regulators are really going to rule the day. Covetous Crew always yipped about dominating Rallos Zek, well, on Race War it will be a near reality!
<P>You get two or three 20-25th level characters into Infected Paw and you've effectively halted all leveling in that dungeon for an evening. There's no better way to dominate than to keep your foes low.
<P>(The ironic thing is that all those blue players seem to think Race War is going to be the panacea of roleplaying ... when in fact Race War is going to attract the vicious PKs and Naked Mages in droves. The REWARDS are so much greater and the risk so much lower.)
<P>On the bright side ... maybe when Verant fixes Race WAr, it will ACTUALLY fix all the problems with Rallos Zek (same codebase, hopefully) we've been telling them about for the last two months.
<P>H -- a proud Rallos Zek player who knows Race War is not the be-all and end-all.
<BR>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
